<p>Dear Customer, </p>
 
<p>Please review and retain the following order information for your records. </p>

=========================================================== <br />
Orden Número <%= @order.number %> <br />
Order Summary<br />
=========================================================== <br />
<% for item in @order.line_items %>
<%=item.variant.sku %> <%=item.variant.product.name%> <%= item.variant.options_text -%> (<%=item.quantity%>) @ <%= number_to_currency item.price %> = <%= number_to_currency(item.price * item.quantity) %> <br />
<% end %>
=========================================================== <br />
<p>Subtotal: <%= number_to_currency @order.item_total %> <br />
<% @order.adjustments.each do |adjustment| %>
<%= "#{adjustment.label}: #{number_to_currency adjustment.amount}"%> <br />
<% end %>
Order Total: <%= number_to_currency @order.total %> </p>

<p>Su orden está siendo procesada... </p>


Gracias por su compra!!!!
